<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>🏇 クイズダービー</title>
<meta name="description" content="班対抗でコインを賭けて競うクイズゲーム">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#f5c518">
<link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon-192.png">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Maru+Gothic:wght@400;700;900&family=Kaisei+Decol:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --dark: #0d1117;
  --card: #161b22;
  --border: #30363d;
  --text: #e6edf3;
  --text-dim: #8b949e;
  --gold: #f5c518;
  --green: #3fb950;
  --green-light: #7ee787;
  --red: #f85149;
  --blue: #58a6ff;
}
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
body {
  font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.6;
  min-height: 100vh;
}
.container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
.header {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 30px 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f2e 0%, #0d1117 100%);
  border-bottom: 3px solid var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.logo {
  font-family: 'Kaisei Decol', serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,197,24,.3);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.subtitle { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: .95rem; }

/* SCREEN */
.screen { display: none; }
.screen.active { display: block; }

/* CARD */
.card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.card-title {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.info-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
}
.tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: .85rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.tag-g { background: var(--green); color: var(--dark); }
.tag-b { background: var(--blue); color: var(--dark); }
.dim { color: var(--text-dim); }

/* BUTTON */
.btn {
  padding: 12px 28px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s;
}
.btn-gold {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
}
.btn-gold:hover {
  background: #ffd700;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(245,197,24,.4);
}
.btn-ghost {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text);
}
.btn-ghost:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold);
  color: var(--gold);
}
.btn-sm { padding: 8px 18px; font-size: .9rem; }
.btn-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* CONFIG SCREEN */
.config-section {
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.config-label {
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}
.config-input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 1rem;
}
.race-config-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.race-config-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr 100px;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
}

/* SETUP */
.horse-input {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.h-num {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.horse-input input {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

/* ROULETTE */
.roulette-window {
  height: 240px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  background: var(--dark);
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.roulette-pointer {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: calc(100% - 20px);
  height: 80px;
  border: 3px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 8px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 10;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(245,197,24,.5);
}
.roulette-drum {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 80px 0;
}
.rl-item {
  height: 80px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.rl-item.selected {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
}
.roulette-result {
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #ffd700 100%);
  color: var(--dark);
  border-radius: 12px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(245,197,24,.4);
}
.roulette-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.rl-list-item {
  padding: 12px;
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.rl-list-item.selected {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
  border-color: var(--gold);
}

/* ODDS BOARD */
.odds-board {
  background: var(--dark);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.odds-head {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 50px 2fr 1fr 1fr 2fr;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px;
  background: rgba(245,197,24,.1);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: .85rem;
  color: var(--gold);
}
.odds-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 50px 2fr 1fr 1fr 2fr;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  align-items: center;
}
.odds-val {
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}
.odds-val.low { color: var(--green-light); }
.odds-val.high { color: var(--red); }
.bar-wrap {
  background: var(--border);
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--gold);
  transition: width .3s;
}

/* BETTING */
.team-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.team-card {
  padding: 16px;
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 2px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s;
  text-align: center;
}
.team-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
.team-card.active {
  border-color: var(--gold);
  background: rgba(245,197,24,.1);
}
.team-card.confirmed {
  border-color: var(--green);
  background: rgba(63,185,80,.1);
}
.team-card.no-coins {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  border-color: var(--red);
}
.team-name {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.team-coins {
  font-size: .85rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
}
.bet-panel {
  background: var(--dark);
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.remain-tag {
  background: rgba(245,197,24,.1);
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.bet-horse-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr));
  gap: 10px;
}
.bet-horse-btn {
  padding: 12px;
  background: var(--card);
  border: 2px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.bet-horse-btn:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold);
}
.bet-horse-btn.active {
  border-color: var(--gold);
  background: rgba(245,197,24,.1);
}
.coin-ctrl {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
}
.c-btn {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s;
}
.c-btn:hover {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
}
.c-num {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--gold);
  min-width: 60px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* RACE */
.timer-wrap {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 30px 0;
}
.timer-display {
  font-size: 6rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-family: 'Kaisei Decol', serif;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(245,197,24,.3);
  transition: color .3s;
}
.timer-display.warn {
  color: #ffd700;
}
.timer-display.danger {
  color: var(--red);
  animation: pulse 1s infinite;
}
#goal-overlay {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,.9);
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 1000;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}
.goal-text {
  font-size: 6rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-family: 'Kaisei Decol', serif;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(245,197,24,.6);
  animation: pulse 1s infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
}

/* SCORE INPUT */
.score-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.score-card {
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
.score-card input {
  width: 80px;
  padding: 8px;
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
}

/* RESULT */
.podium {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 16px;
  margin: 30px 0;
}
.podium-place {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 16px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  min-width: 140px;
}
.p1 {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700 0%, #f5c518 100%);
  color: var(--dark);
  order: 2;
  transform: translateY(-20px);
}
.p2 {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c0c0c0 0%, #a8a8a8 100%);
  color: var(--dark);
  order: 1;
}
.p3 {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cd7f32 0%, #b8751f 100%);
  color: var(--dark);
  order: 3;
}
.p-rank {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.p-name {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.p-score {
  font-size: 1rem;
  opacity: .8;
}
.res-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.res-table th {
  background: rgba(245,197,24,.1);
  color: var(--gold);
  padding: 12px;
  text-align: left;
  font-weight: 700;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
}
.res-table td {
  padding: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.res-table tr.r1 { background: rgba(255,215,0,.1); }
.res-table tr.r2 { background: rgba(192,192,192,.1); }
.res-table tr.r3 { background: rgba(205,127,50,.1); }
.payout-card {
  background: var(--dark);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.payout-team {
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.payout-amount {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 900;
}
.payout-amount.win { color: var(--green-light); }
.payout-amount.lose { color: var(--red); }

/* FINAL */
.champion-banner {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #ffd700 100%);
  color: var(--dark);
  padding: 40px 20px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(245,197,24,.4);
}
.champ-label {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.champ-name {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-family: 'Kaisei Decol', serif;
}
/* SLIDER */
#coin-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  appearance: none;
  width: 24px;
  height: 24px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(245,197,24,.5);
}
#coin-slider::-moz-range-thumb {
  width: 24px;
  height: 24px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(245,197,24,.5);
}
/* HELP BUTTON */
.help-btn {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 20px;
  right: 20px;
  width: 56px;
  height: 56px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
  border: none;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(245,197,24,.4);
  z-index: 1000;
  transition: transform .2s;
  pointer-events: auto;
}
.help-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
.help-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
/* HOW TO PLAY */
.howto-step {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.howto-num {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--dark);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 32px;
  margin-right: 12px;
}
.howto-title {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.howto-desc {
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-size: .9rem;
}
.tips-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,197,24,.1) 0%, rgba(245,197,24,.05) 100%);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.tips-title {
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">🏇 クイズダービー</div>
    <div class="subtitle">Quiz Derby Game</div>
  </div>

  <!-- HELP BUTTON -->
  <button class="help-btn" onclick="toggleHelp()" id="help-btn" title="遊び方">？</button>

  <!-- HOW TO PLAY SCREEN -->
  <div class="screen" id="scr-howto">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">📖 遊び方</div>
      
      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">1</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">⚙️ 準備</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">レース数・班数・初期コイン・解答時間を設定</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">2</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">🎰 ルーレット</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">お題をルーレットで決定（カスタムで自由入力も可能）</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">3</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">🪙 投票</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">各班がコインを賭ける。オッズが表示されるので戦略的に！</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">4</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">🏁 レース</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">参加者がお題に沿ってクイズに答える（制限時間内）</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">5</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">🏆 結果</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">正解数で順位決定。的中した班に配当が入る！</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howto-step">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start">
          <span class="howto-num">6</span>
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="howto-title">👑 優勝</div>
            <div class="howto-desc">全レース終了後、最もコインを持っている班が優勝🎉</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tips-box">
        <div class="tips-title">💡 コツ</div>
        <ul style="margin-left:20px;color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.8">
          <li>オッズが高い馬は当たると大きい配当！</li>
          <li>スライダーで素早く投票できます</li>
          <li>全部賭けるとハイリスク・ハイリターン</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top:24px">
        <button class="btn btn-gold" onclick="closeHelp()">ゲームを始める</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ SCREEN: CONFIG ═══ -->
  <div class="screen active" id="scr-config">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">⚙️ ゲーム設定</div>
      
      <div class="config-section">
        <div class="config-label">レース数</div>
        <input type="number" class="config-input" id="race-count" value="4" min="1" max="10">
      </div>

      <div class="config-section">
        <div class="config-label">班の数</div>
        <input type="number" class="config-input" id="team-count" value="14" min="1" max="30">
      </div>

      <div class="config-section">
        <div class="config-label">初期コイン（班ごと）</div>
        <input type="number" class="config-input" id="initial-coins" value="5" min="1" max="100">
      </div>

      <div class="config-section">
        <div class="config-label">解答時間（秒）</div>
        <input type="number" class="config-input" id="race-time" value="60" min="30" max="300">
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-gold" onclick="startConfig()">次へ：レース詳細設定</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ SCREEN: RACE CONFIG ═══ -->
  <div class="screen" id="scr-race-config">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">📋 各レースの設定</div>
      <div id="race-config-list"></div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-gold" onclick="finishRaceConfig()">設定完了：ゲーム開始</button>
        <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="backToConfig()">戻る</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ SCREEN: SETUP ═══ -->
  <div class="screen" id="scr-setup">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">📝 出走馬の名前入力</div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="tag tag-g" id="setup-race-label">第1レース</span>
